{"tid":1916622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚詠麟頭號鐵粉肥萍因病離世","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T05:26:59.000Z","uid":22556,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"173a3d88f795a018f0130607fce69b1950bbbd19","tid":1916622,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:41:21.000Z","msg":"樂壇校長譚詠麟（阿倫）擁有無數粉絲，當年鐵粉阿萍更是如影相隨，每次阿倫出席公開活動，阿萍總喺佢左右，不過近年阿倫比較少露面，而阿萍近年也有支持其他歌手的活動，間中也有出現。早前阿萍病重入院，直至今午離世，阿倫助手回覆東網表示已知阿萍死訊說：「佢喺醫院留醫時已知道。我哋有同佢屋企人聯絡過，不過詳細情況，譚生話唔回應啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200308/mobile/bkn-20200308170700997-0308_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200308%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200308170700997-0308_00862_001.html&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM7ccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=79bad360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200308/mobile/bkn-20200308170700997-0308_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"853cd8b41ae163a6c307eef7cdf8d76d45aa9818","tid":1916622,"uid":31637,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"皺皮倫都差唔多架啦<br />\n好快可以係地獄見到自己既偶像"},{"pid":"b537ef8cea3930d001ef571e0609d1a1ea13038d","tid":1916622,"uid":260764,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"支倫食歌迷食唔中肥萍"},{"pid":"692ed19642e7a9f9af2491a5a61256b344cc8988","tid":1916622,"uid":315761,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"希望譚詠麟可以早日落去探肥萍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d9b95c1d07f56dbffde999094f60750b570392","tid":1916622,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"692ed19642e7a9f9af2491a5a61256b344cc8988","tid":1916622,"uid":315761,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy"